## Authentication

{% if has_authentication %}
{% if auth_type == 'jwt' %}
### JWT Bearer Token

Include the token in the Authorization header:
```
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

### Obtain Token
```http
POST /api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
    "access_token": "eyJ...",
    "token_type": "bearer",
    "expires_in": 1800
}
```
{% elif auth_type == 'api_key' %}
### API Key

Include the API key in the header:
```
X-API-Key: <your_api_key>
```
{% endif %}
{% else %}
This API does not require authentication.
{% endif %}

## Endpoints

{% if has_health_check %}
### Health Check

```http
GET /health
```

**Response:**
```json
{
    "status": "healthy",
    "service": "{{ project_name }}",
    "version": "{{ project_version }}"
}
```
{% endif %}

### List Items

```http
GET /api/v1/items?skip=0&limit=10
```

**Query Parameters:**
| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|---------|-------------|
| skip | int | 0 | Items to skip |
| limit | int | 10 | Max items (1-100) |

**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "data": [
        {"id": 1, "name": "Item 1", "description": "..."}
    ],
    "total": 100,
    "skip": 0,
    "limit": 10
}
```

### Get Item

```http
GET /api/v1/items/{item_id}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "data": {"id": 1, "name": "Item 1", "description": "..."}
}
```

### Create Item

```http
POST /api/v1/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "New Item",
    "description": "Item description"
}
```

**Response (201):**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Item created successfully",
    "data": {"id": 1, "name": "New Item", "description": "..."}
}
```

### Update Item

```http
PUT /api/v1/items/{item_id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Item",
    "description": "Updated description"
}
```

### Delete Item

```http
DELETE /api/v1/items/{item_id}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Item deleted successfully"
}
```

## Error Responses

### 400 Bad Request
```json
{"success": false, "error": "BAD_REQUEST", "detail": "Invalid input"}
```

### 401 Unauthorized
```json
{"success": false, "error": "UNAUTHORIZED", "detail": "Invalid credentials"}
```

### 404 Not Found
```json
{"success": false, "error": "NOT_FOUND", "detail": "Item not found"}
```

### 422 Validation Error
```json
{
    "detail": [
        {"loc": ["body", "name"], "msg": "field required", "type": "value_error.missing"}
    ]
}
```

### 500 Internal Server Error
```json
{"success": false, "error": "INTERNAL_ERROR", "detail": "An error occurred"}
```

